==English==
===Verb===
'''[[fish]] [[or]] [[cut]] [[bait]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[choose]] between taking action now, or foregoing the opportunity and putting that energy into another endeavor; to [[decide]].
#:''It's time to '''fish or cut bait''': either we buy this house now, or we must start looking for another one.''

